text = "Two-town world sim: towns are SettlementTown nodes with facilities, activity points, territories, road paths, and no-build town borders. Right-click debug blocks to advance time, change food/occupancy, force a raid, or show faction territories/town borders/roads. Floating town labels show food, pressure, population, occupancy, and current action."
